{"tid":2182832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警民口角向孕婦噴椒 並將孕婦拉跌 附近有血跡","createTime":"2020-08-31T14:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T15:50:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":60,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"0ace5f7c1c93a0664c32eb867e67cba4c2010ab9","tid":2182832,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:24:56.000Z","msg":"【831一周年 警民口角向孕婦噴椒 並將孕婦拉跌】<br />\n<br />\n約晚上10點，在亞皆老街彌敦道交界附近，百老匯對出的位置，有一名孕婦及其伴侶與警方發生口角，其間有警員向兩位噴射胡椒噴霧，引致場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n混亂期間有警員將孕婦拉跌。據現場記者所見，該名孕婦倒地後附近有血跡，但未能確定血的出處。<br />\n<br />\n攝/ Jason Wong<br />\n<br />\n#DBC #DBChannel #加山傳播 #太子 #831一周年 #加攝 #香港 #香港警察<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/317787926304280/?extid=VFYlxviN1BhvtbqV&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109301110486297%2Fposts%2F317787926304280%2F%3Fextid%3DVFYlxviN1BhvtbqV%26d%3Dn&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=8b0be4ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109301110486297/posts/317787926304280/?extid=VFYlxviN1BhvtbqV&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1e47d03511ea564e3ac273a91213c8f830c24cf4","tid":2182832,"uid":72361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e50636c4e25b9328d2a0f017cabf13603ae6a9fb","tid":2182832,"uid":284708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />dklm popo無人性"},{"pid":"e1253ecdb4aa559e7b532fe5a421688feab90e9d","tid":2182832,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51b02177a697ddf8f8a795b80708f7c74a4b6c88","tid":2182832,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a